meico.msm

Class Goto

  • java.lang.Object
    • meico.msm.Goto

  • public class Goto
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a helper class for processing MSM sequencingMaps. It is used to represent goto elements from msm sequencingMaps, used in methods Msm.applySequencingMapToMap() and Mei.processEnding().
    Author:
    Axel Berndt.
